committee/&quot;>;2015 年和 2016 年俄罗斯对民主党全国委员会进行的网络攻击&lt;/a>;。截至周四晚上，...&lt;/p >; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/19/24201864/crowdstrike-outage-explained-microsoft-windows-bsod&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p >; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/19/24201864/crowdstrike-outage-explained-microsoft-windows-bsod" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/19/24201864/crowdstrike-outage-explained-microsoft-windows-bsod</id><author><name>艾玛·罗斯</name></author></entry></feed>